{"id":92,"count":1,"description":"Classical Odisha \u2013 A land where culture, spirituality, and heritage come alive, Odisha is one of India\u2019s most fascinating destinations. Known for its magnificent temples like the Sun Temple at Konark and the sacred Jagannath Temple in Puri, Odisha offers a deep dive into India\u2019s classical architecture and traditions. The golden beaches of Puri, the tranquil beauty of Chilika Lake with its migratory birds and dolphins, and the tribal culture of Odisha add to its charm. Famous for its classical dance form, Odissi, colorful festivals, and rich handicrafts, Odisha is truly a timeless journey into India\u2019s spiritual and cultural heart.","link":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/destinations\/classical-odisa\/","name":"CLASSICAL ODISA","slug":"classical-odisa","taxonomy":"destination","parent":0,"meta":[],"thumbnail":{"width":900,"height":596,"file":"2025\/09\/CLASSICAL-ODISA.png","filesize":1030623,"sizes":{"medium":{"file":"CLASSICAL-ODISA-300x199.png","width":300,"height":199,"filesize":96417,"mime_type":"image\/png","source_url":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/CLASSICAL-ODISA-300x199.png"},"thumbnail":{"file":"CLASSICAL-ODISA-150x150.png","width":150,"height":150,"filesize":38373,"mime_type":"image\/png","source_url":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/CLASSICAL-ODISA-150x150.png"},"medium_large":{"file":"CLASSICAL-ODISA-768x509.png","width":768,"height":509,"filesize":530594,"mime_type":"image\/png","source_url":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/CLASSICAL-ODISA-768x509.png"},"trip-thumb-size":{"file":"CLASSICAL-ODISA-374x226.png","width":374,"height":226,"filesize":134153,"mime_type":"image\/png","source_url":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/CLASSICAL-ODISA-374x226.png"},"destination-thumb-size":{"file":"CLASSICAL-ODISA-600x596.png","width":600,"height":596,"filesize":